---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const downloads = [
  {
    name: 'Intelliremote',
    logo: '/downloads/intelliremote-logo.png',
    file: '/downloads/intelliremote.zip',
    description:
      'Intelliremote is a software application that grants you full remote command over your Home Theater PC\'s infrared or radio frequency remote, unleashing its full capabilities.',
  },
  {
    name: 'MonkeyTunes',
    logo: '/downloads/monkeytunes-logo.png',
    file: '/downloads/monkeytunes.zip',
    description:
      'MonkeyTunes is a Digital Audio Control Protocol (DACP) Server for MediaMonkey to allow remote control of your music anywhere in your house.',
  },
];
---

<BaseLayout title="Downloads" description="Free downloads from Melloware — Intelliremote and MonkeyTunes.">
  <h1>Downloads</h1>

  <p>
    Over the course of several years, I marketed software for both PC and mobile platforms,
    specializing in addressing industry gaps, particularly within the realm of Home Automation.
    However, as time has passed, major corporations like Samsung, Google, Amazon, and others
    have ventured into this domain, leaving little room for smaller independent players,
    including myself. Consequently, my sales gradually declined.
  </p>

  <p>
    I'd like to express my gratitude to all those who supported my software in the past.
    Today, I am making it available for <strong>FREE</strong> download!
  </p>

  <ul class="download-list">
    {downloads.map(d => (
      <li class="download-item">
        <img src={d.logo} alt={d.name} class="download-logo" />
        <div class="download-content">
          <h2>{d.name}</h2>
          <p>{d.description}</p>
          <a href={d.file} class="download-btn" download>
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4" />
              <polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10" />
              <line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3" />
            </svg>
            Download {d.name}
          </a>
        </div>
      </li>
    ))}
  </ul>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h1 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .download-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 2rem 0 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .download-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .download-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .download-logo {
    width: 80px;
    height: auto;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .download-content {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .download-content h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .download-content p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .download-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.45rem 1rem;
    background-color: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: background-color 0.15s;
  }

  .download-btn:hover {
    background-color: var(--accent-hover);
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
</style>
